Review_Text: I was shocked and amused at the same time at the last scene and then I couldn't stop laughing. Overall, it was a great documentary on everything sex. Parts of it were actually educational, some were entertaining. Sexual muppets are the best thing I've ever seen. Watch this document and learn something. I definitely learned about how to stimulate properly a vagina and a penis.I would have liked to see more hetero representation but overall they gave us great tips on how to have a great sex life and taught us that sex positivity is a good thing!
